    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harold they're destroying the universe</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/ffe7ad8a6459ab793206e0e6f873eb32.poster.avif?t=1753419985\" width=593 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/ffe7ad8a6459ab793206e0e6f873eb32.webm?t=1753419985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/07f99907bd7aca824dc183e564b8c2e8.avif?t=1753419985\" width=524 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Until Oblivion</strong> is a slightly horrific narrative game that follows 17 year old nobody <strong>Emma Wilson</strong> as she tries to rekindle a dying relationship in a dying world. Join her in an increasingly nightmarish Halloween party and find out if anything (or anyone) is worth anything at all. Featuring an atmospheric hand-crafted world, striking gothic imagery, and teenage takes on faith, work, and interpersonal relationships, Until Oblivion is a unique psychological experience whose horror is only usurped by its heart. And there are lesbians.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.5D stylized artwork</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive dialogue with branching paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Themes of loneliness, love, and loss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time-loop yuri</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually building horror</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark secrets and hidden lore</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He's watching you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/f832940781818c63501f0099cc186c63.webp?t=1753419985\" width=540 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flashing lights, bright colors, mild gore, implied self harm, mild jumpscares, disturbing imagery, depictions of hallucinations/insanity, swearing, possibly grating noises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/9b6c1b8d0f8b54bebb541e4f733b55c6.avif?t=1753419985\" width=530 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I would like to honor the following people who helped during the development process, and whose contributions made this game a reality:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oli</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Remmy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lily</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vivian</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for reading and checking out my game's page. This game is a pure passion project of mine and will always be 100% free, but you can help out by wishlisting if you're interested!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106660/extras/204da67d746c057990af6041ab685faf.avif?t=1753419985\" width=491 height=440 /></span></p>",
